*******************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************
     Readme File for STT of the X-Ray Telescope Advanced Example
*******************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************

STT testing of XrayTel should contain the following:

gmake
XrayTel test.mac

this should produce one output file:
xraytel.out (0.5 kbytes)

This should be compared with 
xraytel_ref.out

The job should take ~ 2 minutes on a 1 GHz Linux machine

Platforms to be tested on:
LINUX

NOTE: with the new physics the example does not produce any output (unless it is run with much higher statistics)

G4ANALYSIS_USE requires an AIDA implementation 
In this case 
- computation time ~ 4 minutes
- the file xraytel.hbook is created (~250 kbytes)
- this file should be compared to xraytel_ref.hbook

Giovanni Santin
e-mail: giovanni.santin@esa.int

*******************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************
